title: Approved Housing Bodies) Act 2019 (No. 47 of 2019) hereby orders as follows:
heading: 2. The 8th day of June 2020 is appointed as the day on which the following
text_raw:
2. The 8th day of June 2020 is appointed as the day on which the following 
provisions of the Housing (Regulation of Approved Housing Bodies) Act 2019 
(No. 47 of 2019) shall come into operation: 

(a) 

(b) 

sections 1 and 2; 

subsections (1), (2), (3) and (4) of section 11. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Minister for Housing, 
Planning and Local Government, 

22 May, 2020. 

EOGHAN MURPHY, 

Minister for Housing, Planning and Local Government. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 29th May, 2020.
